org.sakaiproject.entitybroker.entityprovider.capabilities

Interface Redirectable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EntityProvider
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RedirectControllable, RedirectDefinable, RESTful
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionsEntityProviderMock, AnnouncementEntityProviderImpl, ChatChannelEntityProvider, ForumMessageEntityProviderImpl, ForumTopicEntityProviderImpl, MembershipEntityProvider, PollEntityProvider, PollOptionEntityProvider, PollVoteEntityProvider, ProfileEntityProvider, ProfileLinkEntityProvider, RedirectableEntityProviderMock, RedirectControllableEntityProviderMock, RedirectDefineableEntityProviderMock, RequestStoreableEntityProviderMock, RESTfulEntityProviderMock, SessionEntityProvider, SiteEntityProvider, SynopticMsgcntrItemEntityProviderImpl, UserEntityProvider, UserPrefsEntityProvider

    public interface Redirectable
extends EntityProvider
    This entity type has the ability to define and handle configurable URLs, URLs like this can be handled and supported:
    /gradebook/7890/student/70987 to view all the grades for a student from a course
    /gradebook/6758/item/Quiz1 to view a particular item in a gradebook by it's human readable name
    /gradebook/item/6857657 to maybe just a view an item by its unique id.
    Works with the EntityURLRedirect annotation
    This is the convention interface
    This is one of the capability extensions for the EntityProvider interface
    Author:
    Aaron Zeckoski (azeckoski @ gmail.com)
    See Also:
    EntityURLRedirect
